                        h3.c-entry__heading Empathy isn’t about being nice but it can help increase revenue.

                        a.c-entry__link(href="https://vimeo.com/343056801" target="_blank")
                            address.c-entry__author Vimeo • 99U


                            section.c-entry__content
                                h4.c-entry__content__heading Michael Ventura: Empathy is your Best Creative Tool
                                
                                p.c-entry__content__blurb Entrepreneur and author Michael Ventura has dedicated his career to exploring how empathy can make us better leaders, collaborators, and contributors to society. In his 99U talk, Michael explains that the practice of empathy “isn’t about being nice” — it’s about deep understanding, and learning to apply that understanding to incredibly effective ends.








        


    